{"tid":259622,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人對安鼻寧上左癮？","createTime":"2017-05-27T05:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T15:14:32.000Z","uid":53515,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a5bc1a4fa16167c54f0b9b7a289d50c53e1b9897","tid":259622,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:43:31.000Z","msg":"香港人對鼻敏感應該唔陌生，我係塞到完全抖唔到氣。睇左幾皮嘢專科都醫唔好。<br />\n偶然買左一支安鼻寧就返唔到轉頭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/133844_1b8ebaf978e1ee9ccb35f74541498422.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F133844_1b8ebaf978e1ee9ccb35f74541498422.jpg&h=7a6ebe62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢支嘢噴一次有效12個鐘，我已經用左兩年幾。<br />\n最近效力開始得返幾個鐘，再睇說明書先知唔可以連續用多過7日。<br />\n<br />\n依家唔噴根本抖唔到氣，有時瞓瞓下塞醒左第日想死咁，只好瞓前點都噴一嘢。<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打知點斷尾？運動以外。"},{"pid":"be8eb5fcd6307fba09b28c60297314bd78827be6","tid":259622,"uid":9328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:47:30.000Z","msg":"次次一噴完就瘋狂流鼻水, 用過幾次就無用"},{"pid":"3acab660965a7f5c81efe4de123d85d0070a0faf","tid":259622,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:50:42.000Z","msg":"用過泰國出品果支薄荷鼻塞未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一吸簡直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615a0d412b3a35442b44750162f76bd9f77aa3df","tid":259622,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:55:37.000Z","msg":"有冇塞得咁夸<br />\n🙄"},{"pid":"259c38f038ee5c0bb90fbba30a8f50b2ed90e828","tid":259622,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:59:35.000Z","msg":"用左個下真係好爽 好似個世界係你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但一過左藥力之後 仲慘過未噴之前"},{"pid":"b286bea2cb49dcb2bc9f